flowchart TD
    GOAL([Bounded engineering goal]) --> PLAN[Create plan and constraints]
    PLAN --> SELECT[Select next tool or action]
    SELECT --> EXEC[/Execute in permitted environment/]
    EXEC --> OBSERVE[/Observe result and side effects/]
    OBSERVE --> VERIFY{{Goal and safety checks pass?}}
    VERIFY -->|No, recoverable| REVISE[Revise plan or rollback]
    REVISE --> SELECT
    VERIFY -->|No, uncertain or unsafe| ESC[[Escalate to human]]
    VERIFY -->|Yes| REPORT[Report evidence and proposed outcome]
    REPORT --> APPROVE([Human approval or governed acceptance])
